parameters.name: SC_X
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft heliocentric X position in Heliographic (RTN) coordinates in units of astronomical units.

parameters.name: SC_Y
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft heliocentric Y position in Heliographic (RTN) coordinates in units of astronomical units.

parameters.name: SC_Z
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft heliocentric Z position in Heliographic (RTN) coordinates in units of astronomical units.

parameters.name: VEL_X
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity heliocentric X component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Y
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity heliocentric Y component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Z
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity heliocentric Z component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: SC_R
parameters.description: Column contains Sun to spacecraft range in units of astronomical units.

parameters.name: SC_LAT
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft IHG latitude measured from the solar equatorial plane (positive above the plane) in degrees.

parameters.name: SC_LON
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft IHG longitude (increasing in the direction of planetary orbital motion) in degrees.

parameters.name: SOLAR_EQUATORIAL_TO_HG
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Solar Equatorial to Heliographic coordinates.

parameters.name: HG_TO_EARTHORBTRUE
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Heliographic to Earth Orbit True coordinates.

parameters.name: SPACECRAFT_TO_HG
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Payload (Spacecraft) to Heliographic coordinates.
